description:
WP comics is a UK comic publisher founded by Mark Fluharty. WP Comics publishes comics and graphic novels and is the publisher of two comic anthologies co-founded by Mark Fluharty and Kim Roberts called The Chronicles of Terror and Tales From Orbit.

WP comics has a range of titles including Eagleburger, Radiation Burn, The World Hates Jimmy, Mac and Trouble, Funny Business, Ultra Minion and Recollection.
name: WP Comics Ltd.

description:
We're a group of four comics authors living in north-eastern Italy. Towards the end of 2013 we opened our Facebook page and started publishing some webcomics. In 2014 we started a collaboration with the videogame publisher Devolver Digital and so far we've worked together on comics for Hotline Miami 2, Gods Will Be Watching and Ronin. In 2015 the French publisher Clair De Lune started publishing our series Rosaviola, drawn by Cinzia Di Felice. Recently we self-published the print editions of some of our projects in Italian, and we sell them at comics conventions in Italy and on our online store. (Source)
